Take a deep breath and prepare for a tranquil journey
through the seasons with Storm, an atmospheric, ethereal
experience where you use natural phenomena to guide a
simple seed to fertile soil so it can take root and
spring to life.
Embrace the subtleties and strengths of nature to move a
broken branch, fill a small pond or make snow fall to
solve puzzles and create natural paths. Take your time
and explore nature's nooks or simply enjoy the ambiance
as you float, blow and bounce a seed to the perfect
place to take root. Relax and enjoy Adventure, Challenge
or Spirit modes, each set in gorgeous environments and
enhanced by soothing, nature-inspired soundscapes.
